555 menu-item-parent-archive\" id=\"menu-item-555\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/a-century-of-negro-spirituals-for-solo-voice-the-pioneers/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">A Century of Negro Spirituals</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-642 menu-item-parent-archive\" id=\"menu-item-642\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/25-recommended-recordings-of-negro-spirituals-for-solo-vocalist/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Recommended Recordings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1749 menu-item-parent-archive\" id=\"menu-item-1749\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/composers-brief-biographies/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Brief Biographies</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-1736\" id=\"menu-item-1736\"><a href=\"http://www.artoftheconcertspiritual.com/so-you-want-to-sing-spirituals-extra-content/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">SYWTSS Appendices</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1319 menu-item-parent-archive\" id=\"menu-item-1319\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/spirituals-on-video/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Spirituals Video Playlist</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-442 menu-item-parent-archive\" id=\"menu-item-442\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/related-sites/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Related Resources</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-1043\" id=\"menu-item-1043\"><a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/singin1/negro-spirituals-album-covers/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Album Covers</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-1280 menu-item-parent-archive\" id=\"menu-item-1280\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/the-spiritual-in-poetry-art/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Poetry &amp; Art</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-439 menu-item-parent-archive\" id=\"menu-item-439\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/the-what-and-the-why/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">What, Why &amp; Who</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-1372\" id=\"menu-item-1372\"><a href=\"http://artoftheconcertspiritual.com\"><span class=\"menu-title\">ACS</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav><!-- #menu-secondary -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</header><!-- #header -->\n<div class=\"main\" id=\"main\">\n<div class=\"hgrid-stretch frontpage-grid\">\n<main class=\"content-frontpage\" id=\"content-frontpage\">\n<div class=\"frontpage-area frontpage-page-content frontpage-staticpage-content module-bg-none module-font-theme frontpage-area-boxed\" id=\"frontpage-page-content\">\n<div class=\"hgrid main-content-grid\">\n<div class=\"content hgrid-span-12 no-sidebar layout-full-width\" id=\"content\" itemprop=\"mainContentOfPage\" role=\"main\">\n<div class=\"content-wrap theiaStickySidebar entry-content\" id=\"content-wrap\">\n<article class=\"entry author-ansdiscog post-264 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail\" id=\"post-264\">\n<div class=\"entry-content\" itemprop=\"text\">\n<div class=\"entry-the-content\">\n<p><em><strong><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignright wp-image-1701 size-medium\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"172\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" src=\"https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/LPCDsm-1-300x172.jpg\" srcset=\"https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/LPCDsm-1-300x172.jpg 300w, https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/LPCDsm-1.jpg 404w\" width=\"300\"/>The Spirituals Database</strong></em> offers searchable access to recorded track information for concert Negro Spiritual settings performed by solo Classical vocalists. The resource contains a selection from a century of historic and contemporary concert spiritual recordings produced on compact discs, long-playing (33 1/3 rpm) albums, 78 rpm records, 45 rpm discs, audio cassettes and streamed audio files, as well as demonstration recordings from musical score collections. Additionally, the site offers a number of historical, biographical and bibliographical resources related to this African American music style. There are also links to images, videos and artistic creations inspired by the Negro spiritual.</p>\n<p>Begin searching <em><strong>The Spirituals Database</strong></em> from the simple keyword search box or the advanced search link below:</p>\n<form action=\"/omeka/search\" id=\"search-form\" method=\"get\" name=\"search-form\"><input id=\"query\" name=\"query\" title=\"Search\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/> <input id=\"query_type\" name=\"query_type\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"keyword\"/> <input id=\"record_types\" name=\"record_types[]\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"Item\"/> <input id=\"record_types\" name=\"record_types[]\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"File\"/> <input id=\"record_types\" name=\"record_types[]\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"Collection\"/> <button id=\"submit_search\" name=\"submit_search\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Search\">Search</button></form>\n<p><b><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/omeka/items/search\">Advanced searching</a></b></p>\n<p>Information about advanced search features is available on the <a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/searching-the-database/\" title=\"Searching the Database\">How to Search</a> page.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.artoftheconcertspiritual.com/recorded-solo-concert-spirituals-1916-2022/\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-1695\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"400\" sizes=\"(max-width: 280px) 100vw, 280px\" src=\"https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/RSCSCover-210x300.jpg\" srcset=\"https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/RSCSCover-210x300.jpg 210w, https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/RSCSCover-385x550.jpg 385w, https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/RSCSCover-350x500.jpg 350w, https://spirituals-database.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/RSCSCover.jpg 500w\" width=\"280\"/></a></p>\n<h2>Major Changes to <em>The Spirituals Database</em></h2>\n<p>I developed <strong>The Spirituals Database</strong> in 2015 in order to share research on recordings of concert spirituals for solo vocalists. Even then, however, my eventual goal was to see the results of that research become a printed resource. <a href=\"https://mcfarlandbooks.com/product/recorded-solo-concert-spirituals-1916-2022/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">McFarland and Co.</a> published the book, entitled <strong><a href=\"http://www.artoftheconcertspiritual.com/recorded-solo-concert-spirituals-1916-2022/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Recorded Solo Concert Spirituals, 1916-2022</em></a></strong> on May 4, 2023. One proviso the publisher required, however, was that some of the free content that I offered on <strong>The Spirituals Database</strong> could no longer be available for public access. While this affects the amount of individual track content available here, other information such as images and links to video and audio content will continue to display along with the reduced content. Also, this doesn\u2019t affect Divaslair\u2013that\u2019s me, BTW\u2013videos, slide presentations, or essays posted on <strong>The Spirituals Database</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>The Spirituals Database</strong> and <strong><em>Recorded Solo Concert Spirituals, 1916-2022</em></strong> each function independently. However, each resource supports the other, enhancing the level of available information when combined.</p>\n<p><strong>The Spirituals Database </strong>has undergone numerous changes recently, not only with the addition of uniform titles and more descriptive tags to make the search results even more complete, but with extensive changes to the look and functionality of the database overall. Most recently, my assessments of \u201ccomposer not identified\u201d entries and of dialect use for tracks added to <strong>The Spirituals Database</strong> after <strong><em>Recorded Solo Concert Spirituals, 1916-2022</em></strong> was submitted for publication have now become accessible and searchable. These and other new track entries made after the book was published have a designation of NIB (not in book).</p>\n<h2>What Are Concert Spirituals?</h2>\n<p>Below is a documentary about concert spirituals categorized by song theme, from sorrow songs to songs of transcendence. Each category is followed by a recording by:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u201cI Cannot Stay Here by Myself\u201d (Hall Johnson, composer; A. Grace Lee Mims, soprano)</li>\n<li>\u201cWho\u2019ll Be a Witness for My Lord\u201d (John Rosamond Johnson, composer; Kenneth Spencer, baritone)</li>\n<li>\u201cSteal Away\u201d (Harry T. Burleigh, composer; Martina Arroyo, soprano)</li>\n<li>\u201cGoin\u2019 to Shout All over God\u2019s Heaven\u201d (Clarence Cameron White, composer; Jules Bledsoe, bass)</li>\n<li>\u201cOh, Didn\u2019t It Rain\u201d (Ruby Elzy, soprano)</li>\n<li>\u201cEvery Time I Feel de Spirit\u201d (Lawrence Brown, composer; Evelyn Dove, soprano)</li>\n<li>\u201cMy Soul\u2019s Been Anchored in the Lord\u201d (Florence Price, composer; Marian Anderson, contralto)</li>\n<li>\u201cLet Us Break Bread Together on Our Knees\u201d (Adele Addison, soprano; Fisk Jubilee Singers)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><center></center><center><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_zp94xBtghU\" title=\"YouTube video player\" width=\"560\"></iframe></center></p>\n<h2>SYWTSS Appendices</h2>\n<p>There are several <a href=\"http://www.artoftheconcertspiritual.com/so-you-want-to-sing-spirituals-extra-content/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">appendices</a> originally written for <i>So You Want to Sing Spirituals</i> that are specifically relevant to users of <strong>The Spirituals Database</strong>, especially:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"http://artoftheconcertspiritual.com/SYWTSS/Appendix1-RecommendedRecordings.pdf\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Appendix 1 \u2013 Recommended Recordings</a>:</strong> Selection of recordings recommended for those beginning a collection of concert spirituals for solo voice</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"http://artoftheconcertspiritual.com/SYWTSS/Appendix2-ConcertSpiritualSingersandTheirRecordings.pdf\">Appendix 2 \u2013 Concert Spiritual Singers and Their Recordings</a>:</strong> Sample of singers, arranged by voice type, and their recordings of concert spirituals</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"http://artoftheconcertspiritual.com/SYWTSS/Appendix3-SpiritualsinVocalAnthologiesUPDATED2022.pdf\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Appendix 3 \u2013 Spirituals in Musical Anthologies</a>:</strong> Availability of spirituals in music scores, print publishers, online databases and publishers, self-publishing composers, online resellers, selected musical scores: compilations containing concert spirituals for solo voice</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"http://artoftheconcertspiritual.com/SYWTSS/Appendix4-SongLiteratureClassification.pdf\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Appendix 4 \u2013 Song Literature Classification</a>:</strong> Concert spirituals classified by category with scriptural reference(s) and entry in musical anthologies</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/composers-brief-biographies/\">Appendix 7 \u2013 Composers Brief Biographies</a>:</strong> Short biographies, with score and recordings information, of composers of concert spirituals for solo voice</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Pinterest Page</h2>\n<p>There is a Pinterest page of album and label covers at <a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/singin1/negro-spirituals-album-covers-labels/negro-spirituals/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pinterest.com/singin1/negro-spirituals-album-covers-labels/negro-spirituals/</a>. It\u2019s a bit out-of-date presently, but still of interest.</p>\n</div>\n</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n<div class=\"screen-reader-text\" itemprop=\"datePublished\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Date\">2015-05-17</div>\n</article><!-- .entry -->\n</div><!-- #content-wrap -->\n</div><!-- #content -->\n</div><!-- .main-content-grid -->\n</div>\n</main><!-- #frontpage-content -->\n</div><!-- .frontpage-grid -->\n</div><!-- #main -->\n<div class=\"sub-footer hgrid-stretch inline-nav\" id=\"sub-footer\">\n<div class=\"hgrid\">\n<div class=\"hgrid-span-12\">\n<section class=\"widget widget_nav_menu\" id=\"nav_menu-15\"><div class=\"menu-menu1-container\"><ul class=\"menu\" id=\"menu-menu1\"><li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-home current-menu-item page_item page-item-264 current_page_item menu-item-436 menu-item-parent-archive\"><a aria-current=\"page\" href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">HOME</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-437\"><a href=\"http://spirituals-database.com/omeka/items/search\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Search Database</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-461\"><a href=\"http://spirituals-database.com/omeka/items/browse\"><span class=\"menu-title\">Browse Database</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-438 menu-item-parent-archive\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/searching-the-database/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">How to Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-440 menu-item-parent-archive\"><a href=\"https://spirituals-database.com/the-negro-spiritual/\"><span class=\"menu-title\">